<item>
            <title>[WFLY-5495] Can&apos;t configure ID/data/timestamp columns of JDBC-based cache stores</title>
                <link>https://issues.jboss.org/browse/WFLY-5495</link>
                <project id="12313721" key="WFLY">WildFly</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When I&apos;m trying to configure a JDBC-based cache store for an &quot;offload&quot; Infinispan cache, configuration for the ID/data/timestamp columns is not applied. I found that this is the case by writing:&lt;/p&gt;

